verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, after combination mechanical stretch with hBSMCs / ICCs treatment, the mRNA levels of M2, M3, and c-kit were increased to 5.319 +/-0.346, 3.517 +/-0.245, and 4.581 +/-0.288 (p < 0.001), respectively, whereas the mRNA levels of M2 and M3 for combination mechanical stretch with hBSMCs treatment and combination no stretch with hBSMCs treatment were 3.079 +/-0.273 and 2.574 +/-0.157, and 1.183 +/-0.072 and 1.325 +/-0.061.
